    "source": "my-theme/templates/home.html + all included sections, modules, and CSS files",
    "purpose": "Frozen build blueprint. This file is the single source of truth for the React migration. Every section, DOM structure, content, and style value is specified here. Build exactly this — no redesign, no simplification.",
